### Read all notes
GET http://localhost:3002/api/notes

### Create a new note
POST http://localhost:3002/api/notes
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Backend Homework",
    "content": "Create notes routes with simple CRUD operations.",
    "category": "Study"
}

### Update a note
PUT http://localhost:3002/api/notes/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Updated Shopping List",
    "content": "Buy milk, eggs, bread, coffee and fruit.",
    "category": "Personal"
}

### Delete a note
DELETE http://localhost:3002/api/notes/1
